Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:41.45,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,{Who are Enju and I}Thế Enju và tớ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.62,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,{supposed to fight for?!}phải chiến đấu vì ai chứ?!
